data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7fea4ba-1554-44d0-b59f-7371c0284f4a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Looking%20into%20the%20'brain'%20of%20an%20AI%20model%5C%22%3ELooking%20into%20the%20'brain'%20of%20an%20AI%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20already%20a%20race%20to%20try%20to%20determine%20how%20these%20AI%20chatbots%20spit%20out%20results%20and%20recommendations%2C%20so%20website%20owners%20can%20hack%20their%20way%20to%20better%20online%20distribution%20in%20the%20new%20era%20of%20generative%20AI%20and%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPTrends%20is%20one%20of%20these%20up-and-coming%20AEO%20providers.%20David%20Kaufman%2C%20one%20of%20the%20entrepreneurs%20behind%20the%20firm%2C%20shared%20an%20interesting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fkaufmandak_seo-geo-aisearch-activity-7318996770670190592-FfXQ%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAAAGFo9EBlLjm_yYUTKQr1x3R2iBV2OR4iI4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20AI%20search%20results%20from%20tools%20such%20as%20ChatGPT%20and%20Perplexity%20are%20unpredictable.%20They%20can%20change%20even%20when%20you%20ask%20the%20same%20question%20multiple%20times.%20Unlike%20Google%2C%20where%20search%20results%20stay%20mostly%20the%20same%2C%20AI%20tools%20give%20different%20answers%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20model%20responds%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20Kaufman%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Kaufman%20and%20his%20colleagues%20asked%20ChatGPT%20this%20question%20100%20times%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20best%20support%20ticketing%20software%3F%26quot%3B%20Then%20they%20tracked%20which%20providers%20appeared%20most%20often.%20Here%20are%20the%20results%20of%20the%20test%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20showing%20an%20example%20of%20results%20from%20a%20ChatGPT%20request%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681b9658a466d2b74ab54b21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Kaufman%2C%20GPTrends%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EZendesk%20showed%20up%20in%2094%25%20of%20answers%2C%20while%20other%20companies%2C%20including%20Freshworks%20and%20Zoho%2C%20appeared%20less%20often%20and%20in%20different%20positions.%20This%20randomness%20gives%20less%20well-known%20brands%20a%20better%20shot%20at%20being%20seen%2C%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStrategically%2C%20this%20means%20brands%20need%20to%20rethink%20how%20they%20optimize%20for%20discovery%2C%20focusing%20less%20on%20traditional%20SEO%20tactics%20and%20more%20on%20comprehensive%2C%20authoritative%20content%20that%20AI%20systems%20recognize%20as%20valuable%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaufman%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseo-aeo-ai-chatbots-search-startups-chatgpt-openai-google-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747040461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cfc2b3fe8d3928365551b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseo-aeo-ai-chatbots-search-startups-chatgpt-openai-google-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20chatbots%20like%20Sam%20Altman's%20ChatGPT%20are%20redefining%20online%20discovery%2C%20sparking%20a%20surge%20of%20%26quot%3BAEO%26quot%3B%20startups%20and%20tools.%20It's%20like%20SEO%2C%20but%20for%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseo-aeo-ai-chatbots-search-startups-chatgpt-openai-google-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Termina%20selected%20and%20ranked%20the%202025%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20lists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black-and-white%20portrait%20of%20Jake%20Ellowitz%2C%20a%20smiling%20bald%20man%20wearing%20a%20dark%20zip-up%20sweater%2C%20set%20against%20a%20light%20blue%20background%20with%20a%20bright%20blue%20grid.%20Surrounding%20him%20are%20green%20tech-themed%20icons%2C%20including%20a%20computer%20monitor%2C%20a%20microchip%2C%20and%20binary%20code%20(0s%20and%201s)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681d1841c6ad288d148071b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJake%20Ellowitz%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Termina.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jake%20Ellowitz%2C%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20lists%20are%20created%20based%20on%20data%20analyzed%20by%20Termina.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETermina%20began%20with%20data%20on%20over%201%2C900%20investors%2C%20analyzing%2025%20success%20attributes%2C%20such%20as%20exits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20analysis%20identifies%20skilled%20investors%20with%20a%20high%20likelihood%20of%20continued%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seed%20100%20and%20Seed%2040%20lists%20are%20now%20in%20their%20fifth%20year%20in%20our%20partnership%20with%20Business%20Insider%20to%20objectively%20identify%20and%20celebrate%20the%20success%20of%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20greatest%20seed%20investors.%20In%20the%20run%20of%20these%20releases%2C%20AI%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20defining%20characteristic%20of%20seed-stage%20startups%20today%2C%20the%20results%20of%20which%20will%20likely%20drive%20the%20lists%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20produce%20the%202025%20rankings%2C%20we%20statistically%20analyzed%20seed%20investor%20performance%20in%2025%20areas%20using%20Crunchbase%20and%20PitchBook%20data.%20Since%20one%20of%20our%20goals%20is%20to%20analyze%20the%20prospective%20success%20of%20investors%2C%20rather%20than%20focus%20solely%20on%20past%20achievements%2C%20we%20consider%20only%20active%20investors%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20investments%20between%202010%20and%202025.%20Our%20lists%20include%20solo%20venture%20capitalists%20and%20angel%20investors%20worldwide%2C%20assessed%20based%20on%20their%20investments%20in%20US%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investors%20that%20made%20the%20cut%20for%20the%202025%20lists%20were%20those%20with%20the%20strongest%20long-term%20indicators%3A%20exits%20(initial%20public%20offerings%20or%20acquisitions).%20For%20this%20year's%20ranking%2C%20investors%20whose%20stronger%20indicators%20were%20follow-on%20fundraising%20activity%20have%20had%20their%20positions%20affected%20by%20the%20recent%20pullback%20in%20venture%20capital%20fundraising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20named%20to%20the%20list%2C%20seed%20investors%20must%20have%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EInvestments%20that%20led%20to%20successful%20exits%2C%20including%20IPOs%20or%20acquisitions%20(exits%20that%20were%20meaningfully%20above%20%26quot%3Bliquidation%20preference%26quot%3B%20or%20demonstrated%20increased%20company%20value%20rather%20than%20simply%20raising%20capital).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestments%20that%20display%20intermediate%20signs%20of%20future%20success%2C%20with%20seed%20investments%20consistently%20receiving%20material%20sums%20of%20follow-on%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EActive%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emoderate-to-high%20seed%20investing%20over%20the%20previous%20two%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EExits%20statistically%20have%20the%20most%20influence%20on%20differentiating%20investors.%20We%20also%20updated%20our%20methodology%20this%20year%20to%20weight%20more%20recent%20investments%20for%20the%20intermediate%20milestones%2C%20such%20as%20follow-on%20fundraising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20candidate%20pool%20that%20met%20the%20above%20criteria%20was%201%2C974%20investors%2C%20a%205%25%20increase%20from%20last%20year's.%20Women%20accounted%20for%2011%25%20of%20all%20seed%20investors%20in%20this%20year's%20pool%20%E2%80%94%20up%20from%208%25%20of%20the%20first%20Seed%20100's%20pool%20in%202021.%20This%20final%20list%20included%2026%20investors%20that%20increased%20their%20rank%2C%2027%20with%20the%20same%20or%20lower%20rank%2C%20and%2047%20new%20investors.%20Twenty-seven%20investors%20in%20this%20year's%20ranking%20were%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20original%202021%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22295f39db-91dd-4061-ab28-b4512e133d14%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20generative%20AI%20wave%20of%20seed%20investing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20two%20years%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhistory-of-openai-company-chatgpt-elon-musk-founded-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20its%20revolutionary%20large%20language%20model%20GPT-4%2C%20which%20ignited%20the%20world's%20imagination%20about%20the%20future%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20Having%20AI%20at%20the%20center%20of%20large%20outcomes%20is%20not%20new%3B%20many%20companies%2C%20including%20Alphabet%20and%20Meta%2C%20have%20predicated%20their%20business%20models%20on%20it%20and%20were%20successful%20long%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20segment%20AI%20into%20discriminative%20and%20generative%20models.%20The%20key%20difference%20lies%20in%20their%20objectives.%20Discriminative%20models%20focus%20on%20predicting%20labels%20and%20values%2C%20or%20making%20decisions%20based%20on%20input%20data%2C%20while%20generative%20models%20aim%20to%20capture%20the%20underlying%20data%20distribution%20and%20generate%20samples%20from%20that%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20wave%20of%20seed%20investing%20in%20AI%20was%20from%202010%20to%202018%2C%20during%20which%20companies%20included%20discriminative%20machine%20learning%20in%20their%20general%20business%20models.%20For%20example%2C%20companies%20like%20Uber%2C%20Instacart%2C%20Airbnb%2C%20and%20DoorDash%20were%20built%20on%20discriminative%20matching%20and%20recommendation%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20wave%20of%20AI%20was%20kicked%20off%20by%20generative%20models%2C%20which%20include%20large%20language%20models%20like%20those%20that%20power%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20Alphabet's%20Gemini%2C%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude.%20In%20a%20mere%20two%20years%2C%20the%20share%20of%20companies%20where%20AI%20materially%20matters%20to%20their%20products%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20from%2013%25%20to%2024%25.%20How%20this%20evolves%20will%20likely%20greatly%20influence%20how%20the%20Seed%20100%20rankings%20look%20over%20the%20coming%20years.%20Since%20seed%20investments%20usually%20take%20years%20to%20mature%2C%20we're%20still%20a%20few%20years%20away%20from%20understanding%20how%20the%20new%20wave%20of%20AI%20investments%20will%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20we%20show%20five%20seed%20investment%20categories%20to%20contextualize%20the%20growth%20of%20AI%20investment.%20Note%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20exhaustive%20view%20of%20seed%20investment%20sectors.%20In%20this%20view%2C%20while%20there%20has%20been%20steady%20expansion%20of%20AI%20investing%20at%20the%20seed%20stage%2C%20the%20jump%20last%20year%20stands%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Termina%20Seed%20100%20chart%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cd4bf3fe8d39283654dac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22301%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETermina%20Seed%20100%20chart%202025%3Cp%3ETermina%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJake%20Ellowitz%20is%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapp.termina.ai%2Fauth%2Flogin%2F%5C%22%20t