n%20its%20connections%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20VC%20game.%20And%20there's%20no%20evidence%20that%20any%20of%201789's%20deals%20break%20laws%20prohibiting%20favoritism%20to%20individual%20contractors.%20But%20given%20their%20potential%20for%20creating%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20the%20firm's%20investments%20have%20alarmed%20Washington%20insiders%20familiar%20with%20the%20process.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20lack%20of%20transparency%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20around%20moves%20being%20made%20by%20Musk%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-cuts-federal-worker-firings-government-plan-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20it%20impossible%20to%20tell%20if%20the%20president's%20family%20is%20improperly%20making%20money%20by%20funneling%20government%20business%20to%20the%20companies%20it%20invests%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20certainly%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20appearance%20of%20corruption%2C%20because%20Trump's%20family%20is%20benefiting%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Laura%20Dickinson%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20George%20Washington%20University%20who%20has%20served%20as%20special%20counsel%20for%20the%20Defense%20Department.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you%20look%20at%20this%20in%20the%20context%20of%20arbitrary%20cuts%20to%20other%20programs%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20preferential%20treatment%20is%20being%20given%20to%20family%20and%20others%20who%20curry%20favor%20with%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20legal%20experts%20who%20have%20concerns%20about%20the%20money%20flowing%20to%20Don%20Jr.%20One%20veteran%20Wall%20Street%20investor%2C%20who%20has%20personally%20reviewed%201789's%20deals%2C%20says%20they%20enable%20the%20president's%20son%20to%20profit%20from%20the%20administration's%20actions%2C%20even%20if%20no%20contractors%20are%20given%20preferentia