C%20a%20leading%20watchdog%20group.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20son%20of%20the%20president%20is%20benefiting%20from%20these%20deals%2C%20even%20if%20there's%20a%20few%20degrees%20of%20separation%2C%20is%20there%20a%20level%20playing%20field%3F%20We%20just%20don't%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon%20Jr.'s%20investments%20are%20a%20long%20way%20from%20the%20days%20when%20Washington%20got%20worked%20up%20over%20Jimmy%20Carter's%20brother%20marketing%20his%20own%20beer%20brand.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20old%20enough%20to%20remember%20when%20it%20was%20completely%20shocking%20that%20the%20president's%20brother%20was%20selling%20Billy%20Beer%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nell%20Minow%2C%20the%20vice%20chair%20of%20ValueEdge%20Advisors%2C%20who%20has%20served%20as%20a%20government%20attorney%20at%20the%20EPA%2C%20the%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%2C%20and%20the%20Justice%20Department.%20%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20there%20was%20no%20suggestion%20of%20a%20connection%20to%20access%20or%20policy%20or%20contracts%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20considered%20unseemly.%26quot%3B%20With%201789%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20gone%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level%3A%20This%20is%20a%20flashing%20red%20light%20of%20a%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon%20Jr.%20is%20far%20from%20a%20passive%20bystander%20in%201789.%20According%20to%20Politico%2C%20he%20and%20his%20fellow%20partners%20at%20the%20investment%20firm%20have%20launched%20an%20invite-only%20club%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutive-branch-private-club-details-trump-billionaires-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExecutive%20Branch%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20cost%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%20to%20join.%20Located%20in%20Georgetown%2C%20the%20high-end%20club%20will%20enable%20business%20and%20tech%20moguls%20to%20schmooze%20with%20administration%20insiders%20behind%20closed%20doors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20simultaneously%20creating%20a%20source%20of%20potential%20deals%20for%201789.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20insiders%20who%20have%20worked%20closely%20with%20Trump%20and%20his%20family%20see%20such%20efforts%20as%20improper.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20they're%20doing%20is%20selling%20access%20to%20the%20president%20via%20the%20back%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20someone%20who%20knows%20the%20Trumps%20well.%20%26quot%3BImagine%20for%20one%20second%20if%20Hunter%20Biden%20had%20opened%20this%20club%20while%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20president.%20The%20Republicans%20would%20be%20screaming%20not%20just%20for%20his%20head%2C%20but%20for%20a%20complete%20and%20total%20dismemberment%20of%20his%20body.%20It's%20beyond%20hypocritical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon%20Jr.'s%20involvement%20in%201789%20bears%20an%20eerie%20resemblance%20to%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-political-allies-hunter-biden-acquittal-report-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20blasted%20Hunter%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20doing%3A%20trading%20on%20his%20father's%20name%20to%20win%20lucrative%20business%20deals%20with%20countries%20like%20Ukraine%20and%20China.%20During%20the%202020%20campaign%2C%20Don%20Jr.%20offered%20to%20debate%20Biden%2C%20insisting%20that%20Hunter's%20nepotism%20far%20outstripped%20his%20own.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20say%20I%20haven't%20benefited%20from%20my%20father's%20last%20name%2C%20just%20like%20Hunter%20Biden%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Don%20Jr.%20told%20Axios.%20%26quot%3BThat'd%20be%20foolish%20to%20say%20that.%20But%20I%20haven't%20benefited%20from%20my%20father's%20taxpayer-funded%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20a%20freshly%20minted%20venture%20capitalist%2C%20Don%20Jr.%20is%20explicitly%20gearing%20up%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20next%20four%20years%20of%20his%20father's%20presidency.%20In%20the%20three%20months%20since%20Trump%20was%20inaugurated%2C%201789%20has%20raised%20some%20%24500%20million.%20According%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20the%20firm%20i