ssinsider.com%2Fcountries-with-universal-basic-income%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eidea%20of%20universal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20UBI%2C%20has%20gained%20traction%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20countries%20in%20recent%20years.%20A%20UBI%20is%20when%20a%20government%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecuts%20a%20regular%20check%20to%20its%20entire%20population%20regardless%20of%20financial%20status%20to%20support%2C%20but%20not%20replace%2C%20their%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumerous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foregon-opposition-measure-118-basic-income-corporate-tax-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecities%20and%20counties%20in%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20experimented%20with%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20programs.%20These%20programs%20are%20similar%20to%20a%20UBI%20because%20they%20both%20provide%20no-strings-attached%20payments%2C%20but%20a%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20typically%20goes%20to%20smaller%2C%20low-income%20groups%2C%20or%20vulnerable%20populations%20like%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguaranteed-universal-basic-income-ubi-baltimore-young-families-success-fund-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20moms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-basic-income-program-low-income-black-women-debt-bills-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlack%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudicial-watch-sues-san-francisco-basic-income-program-trans-people-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrans%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20these%20programs%20have%20likened%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bsocialism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20lawmakers%20in%20South%20Dakota%2C%20Iowa%2C%20and%20Idaho%20passed%20laws%20banning%20basic%20income%20programs%20at%20the%20city%20and%20county%20level.%20Republican%20State%20Sen.%20John%20Wiik%2C%20who%20sponsored%20the%20bill%20in%20South%20Dakota%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Senate%20committee%20meeting%20that%20basic%20income%20programs%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bsocialist%20idea%26quot%3B%20that%20redistributes%20people's%20hard-earned%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuaranteed%20income%20programs%2C%20also%20known%20as%20basic%20income%2C%20undercut%20the%20dignity%20in%20earning%20a%20dollar%2C%20and%20they're%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20government%20dependency%2C%26quot%3B%20Wiik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20study%2C%20however%2C%20found%20that%20recipients%20maintained%20steady%20employment%2C%20showed%20improved%20mental%20health%2C%20strengthened%20self-determination%2C%20and%20improved%20financial%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20basic%20income%2C%20people%20actively%20build%20sustainable%20financial%20security%20for%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20and%20also%20spend%20more%20money%20on%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJ%C3%BCrgen%20Schupp%2C%20a%20researcher%20for%20the%20study%2C%20said%20that%20the%20results%2C%20particularly%20those%20related%20to%20labor%2C%20show%20that%20many%20clich%C3%A9s%20about%20universal%20basic%20income%20need%20to%20be%20reconsidered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20for%20the%20urgently%20needed%20restructuring%20of%20social%20systems%2C%20all%20reform%20options%20must%20be%20considered%20%E2%80%94%20including%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-study-germany-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747004068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6821243ea466d2b74ab5a0ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-study-germany-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20G