.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ECool%20Bus%20Stop%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20designed%20using%20climate-responsive%20materials%20and%20tools%20that%20help%20create%20a%20significantly%20cooler%20micro-environment.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20setup%20is%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20high-pressure%20misting%20system.%20It%20releases%20ultra-fine%20mist%20particles%20that%20evaporate%20quickly%2C%20reducing%20the%20ambient%20temperature%20within%20the%20bus%20stop.%20This%20offers%20immediate%20relief%20to%20waiting%20passengers%20and%20introduces%20a%20more%20humane%20and%20climate-conscious%20approach%20to%20everyday%20public%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khus%20curtains%20and%20misting%20systems%20turn%20this%20Ahmedabad%20bus%20stop%20into%20a%20heat-safe%20haven%20for%20daily%20commuters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-86_11zon-1746955760-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-426850%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKhus%20curtains%20and%20misting%20systems%20turn%20this%20Ahmedabad%20bus%20stop%20into%20a%20heat-safe%20haven%20for%20daily%20commuters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20innovation%20uses%20a%20high-pressure%20misting%20system%20that%20creates%20a%20cooling%20effect%20through%20evaporation.%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20is%20pumped%20out%20of%20the%20nozzle%20at%20a%20pressure%20of%200.2%20microns.%20The%20particle%20breaks%20at%20a%20pressure%20of%205%20to%2015%20microns%20and%20creates%20fogging%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Eexplains%20Dipika.%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EShe%20adds%20that%20the%20cool%20bus%20stops%20particularly%20benefit%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20like%20senior%20citizens%20who%20have%20dehydration%20problems%20and%20daily%20wage%20workers%20who%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20physical%20work.%20If%20they%20get%20some%20comfort%2C%20it%20has%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20their%20body%20and%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20innovation%20uses%20less%20energy%20than%20traditional%20air%20cooling%20conditioners%2C%20which%20have%20features%20such%20as%20timers%20and%20adjustable%20pressure.%20It%20also%20ensures%20dust%20suppression%20and%20uses%20khus%20curtains%20to%20ensure%20natural%20cooling%20and%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20between%20the%20hot%20and%20cool%20air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scale%20of%20impact%20is%20remarkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vadgama.%20%E2%80%9COver%20a%20single%20season%2C%20more%20than%206%20lakh%20commuters%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20cooling%20technology.%20When%20you%20calculate%20the%20cost%20per%20person%20served%2C%20it%20emerges%20as%20an%20exceptionally%20economical%20intervention%20for%20heat%20mitigation%20in%20public%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20Cool%20Bus%20Stops%20has%20been%20tremendous.%20The%20Cool%20Bus%20Stop%20consistently%20recorded%20temperatures%205%E2%80%937%20degrees%20lower%20than%20regular%20bus%20stops.%20The%20highest%20temperature%20difference%20of%206.8%20degrees%20was%20observed%20on%2030th%20March%2C%20showcasing%20substantial%20heat%20mitigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20shaded%20area%20will%20provide%20cool%20air%20and%20bring%20relief%20to%20people%20during%20the%20summer.%20It%20will%20help%20protect%20them%20from%20heatstroke%20and%20other%20heat-related%20illnesses.%20I%20sincerely%20congratulate%20the%20AMC%2C%20AMTS%2C%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20team%20for%20this%20initiative.%20I%20hope%20similar%20technology%20will%20be%20implemented%20on%20other%20platforms%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20Shri%20Pratibhaben%20Jain%2C%20Mayor%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20on%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Cool%20Bus%20Stop.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20relaxing%20for%20the%20poor%20people%20like%20us.%20We%20are%20mason%20labors%2C%20and%20using%20this%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Ebus-stop%20regularly%20in%20the%20summer.%20We%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20thing.%20This%20kind%20of%20facility%20is%20really%20good%20for%20the%20people%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20a%20woman%20daily%20wage%20labourer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20first-of-its-kind%20%E2%80%98Cool%20Bus%20Stop%E2%80%99%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20climate%20resilience%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20By%20improving%20comfort%20in%20public%20spaces%2C%20this%20initiative%20sets%20an%20example%20for%20other%20cities%20in%20India%20to%20prioritise%20public%20health%20and%20well-being%20in%20the%20face%20of%20rising%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201536px)%20100vw%2C%201536px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fbanner-1746776121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fbanner-1746776121.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette