ided%20to%20go%20on%20a%20journey%20of%20changing%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20his%20world%2C%20in%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20procure%20raw%20materials%20from%20the%20farmers%2C%20then%20add%20value%20to%20these%20and%20sell%20the%20products%20in%20the%20larger%20market.%20The%20model%20is%20self-sustaining.%20The%20market%20rate%20for%20barley%20is%20Rs%2060%20per%20kg.%20We%20are%20giving%20farmers%20Rs%2075%20per%20kg.%E2%80%9D%20Elaborating%20on%20the%20SHGs%20(self-help%20groups)%20that%20they%20have%20partnered%20with%2C%20Tsetan%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20give%20them%20around%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20we%20purchase%20raw%20materials%20from%20them%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20not%20only%20exemplifies%20how%20one%20can%20drive%20holistic%20community%20growth%20in%20regions%20where%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381089%2Fseed-preservation-andhra-pradesh-darlapudi-ravi-indigenous-local-varieties%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereliance%20on%20a%20traditional%20crop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20also%20how%20one%20can%20do%20so%20sustainably.%20Through%20Siachen%20Naturals%2C%20Tsetan%20is%20ensuring%20that%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20dining%20tables%20keep%20playing%20host%20to%20their%20favourite%20guest%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Cem%3Ethukpa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20for%20years%20to%20come.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Tsetan%20Dorjay%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftecuol.in%2Fevents%2Fgitam-tec-transfers-hybrid-solar-dryer-technology-to-university-of-ladakh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%